{"word":"G3501 - νέος - néos - neh'-os - New","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νέος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">néos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">neh'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">New</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"புது, இளைய, வாலிபரான, புதிதான, புதிய, இளவயதுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. recently born, young, youthful"},{"paragraph":"2. new"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary word, including the comparative (second form); &ldquo;new&rdquo;, that is, (of persons) <i>youthful</i>, or (of things) <i>fresh</i>; figuratively <i>regenerate:</i> - new, young.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3501/3501\">G3501</a>, <a href=\"#/G3502/3502\">G3502</a>, <a href=\"#/G3503/3503\">G3503</a>, <a href=\"#/G3504/3504\">G3504</a>, <a href=\"#/G3555/3555\">G3555</a>, <a href=\"#/G3556/3556\">G3556</a>"}]}